videos.description: Travon Fuller hits Jared Cornelius early on a fair catch and is ejected for a targeting penalty.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Fuller ejected for targeting on a punt

videos.description: Austin Allen finds Jared Cornelius for a six-yard touchdown in the corner of the end zone.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Cornelius hauls in TD catch

videos.description: Texas A&M's Christian Kirk takes advantage of blown coverage to get Texas A&M on the board.
videos.headline: Kirk breaks free for 81-yard TD catch

videos.description: Arkansas' Austin Allen takes a hit on a pass attempt and needs medical attention for a bloody nose on the sideline.
videos.headline: Razorbacks' QB Allen gets hit and suffers bloody nose

videos.description: Cole Kelley finds David Williams open in the end zone for a two-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Razorbacks extend their lead 14-7 with TD

videos.description: Henre' Toliver  intercepts Kellen Mond's pass  to put the Razorbacks in scoring position.
videos.headline: Aggies' pass is intercepted, Razorbacks in scoring position

videos.description: Arkansas extends their lead to 21-7 with a six-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Hayden pushes through defense for TD

videos.description: Aggies' Kellen Mond runs the ball for 79 yards that sets up a Texas A&M field goal.
videos.headline: Texas A&M QB runs 79 yards

videos.description: Travyeon Williams runs down the middle for a 18-yard touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Aggies' Williams runs the ball for TD

videos.description: Bret Bielema discusses how their offense needs to play  more loose, and to stop giving up chunk plays.
videos.headline: Razorbacks Head Coach Bielema talks about offense
ARK VS TA&M

videos.description: Jared Cornelius slips and grabs at his Achilles heel and is taken into the medical tent.
videos.headline: Razorbacks' Cornelius is carried off field

videos.description: Keith Ford runs through the gap and runs the ball in 23 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Ford TD gives Aggies lead

videos.description: Razorbacks David Williams is handed off the ball, and runs up the middle for a one-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Arkansas' Williams runs up the middle for TD

videos.description: Texas A&M's Keith Ford runs 44 yards for touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies' Ford runs 44 yards for TD

videos.description: Arkansas' Austin Allen makes a great throw to Jonathan Nance in double coverage, for a 44-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Razorbacks respond with great TD throw

videos.description: Texas A&M Christian Kirk returns the kickoff for a 100-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Aggies' Kirk with 100-yard kickoff TD

videos.description: Arkansas' David Williams runs through a defender on his way for a four-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Razorbacks' Williams pushes through the end zone for TD

videos.description: Aggies' Kellen Mond's pass is complete to Christian Kirk for the first touchdown in overtime.
videos.headline: Texas A&M with first TD in OT

videos.description: Armani Watts  intercepts Austin Allen's pass in the end zone to  give the Aggies a 50-43 win.
videos.headline: Razorbacks' Allen pass intercepted in end zone to end game

videos.description: Texas A&M coach Kevin Sumlin talks about the penalties in the first half and what it means to win their first SEC game.
videos.headline: Sumlin discusses Aggies' first SEC win

videos.description: ESPN's Brock Huard and Bob Wischusen discuss how Aggies can build their program around Christian Kirk after Texas A&M's 50-43 win over Arkansas.
videos.headline: Aggies can build their program around WR  Kirk

videos.description: In a game that had four lead changes in the fourth quarter, Texas A&M improves to 3-1 on the season with a 50-43 win over Arkansas.
videos.headline: Texas A&M tops Arkansas in OT
